<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Things I Share (Posts by dg-pb)</title><link>https://dg-pb.github.io/</link><description></description><atom:link href="https://dg-pb.github.io/authors/dg-pb.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><language>en</language><copyright>Contents Â© 2025 &lt;a href="mailto:digpob@gmail.com"&gt;dg-pb&lt;/a&gt; </copyright><lastBuildDate>Wed, 08 Oct 2025 06:09:21 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola (getnikola.com)</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>Python's try-finally is simple</title><link>https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/</link><dc:creator>dg-pb</dc:creator><description>&lt;p&gt;Beyond its basic function, there are 2 rules to know:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="code"&gt;&lt;pre class="code python"&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-1" name="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-1" href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-1"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="nd"&gt;@lambda&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;f&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nb"&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;f&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;())&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class="c1"&gt;# 2&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a id="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-2" name="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-2" href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-2"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nf"&gt;finally1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;():&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a id="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-3" name="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-3" href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-3"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;"""&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a id="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-4" name="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-4" href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-4"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;    NOTE:Rule No.1:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a id="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-5" name="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-5" href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-5"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;        The return value of a function is&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a id="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-6" name="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-6" href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-6"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;            determined by the last return&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a id="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-7" name="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-7" href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-7"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;            statement executed.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a id="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-8" name="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-8" href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-8"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;        Since finally clause always&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a id="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-9" name="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-9" href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-9"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;            executes, there can be many return&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a id="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-10" name="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-10" href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-10"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;            statements executed.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a id="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-11" name="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-11" href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-11"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;    """&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a id="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-12" name="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-12" href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-12"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;    &lt;span class="k"&gt;while&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a id="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-13" name="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-13" href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-13"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;        &lt;span class="k"&gt;try&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a id="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-14" name="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-14" href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-14"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;            &lt;span class="k"&gt;try&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a id="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-15" name="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-15" href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-15"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;                &lt;span class="k"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;
