&lt;a id="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-29" name="rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-29" href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_1426fea5a864443582b87dda0734ea42-29"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;            of the finally clause, the&lt;/span&gt;
